Mounting Procedure
==================

You can mount |productP| with VESA mounting (:ref:`guide <vesa_mguide>`): |mount_screws|, enabling simplified installation onto any standard mounting fixture.

You can also mount |productP| with panel mounting method (:ref:`guide <panel_mguide>`).

.. attention::

    Please make sure the display is not exposed to high pressure when mounting into an enclosure.

